.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-7::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  fisherman, photographer, designer, social-worker
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: drama, epic, mystery, spy
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: badminton, cycling, handball, volleyball
1. the person who's sport is volleyball is the person watching epic movies##1
2. the person who's sport is handball is the person watching drama movies##1
3. the person watching mystery movies is on the far left##1
4. the person watching spy movies is on the right of the person watching mystery movies##1
5. the designer is on the left of the person who's sport is badminton##1
6. the photographer is between the person watching epic movies and the person watching mystery movies##2
7. the social-worker is on the left of the person watching drama movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |      3      |    4     |
| Job          | designer  | photographer    | social-worker | fisherman  |
| Movie-Genre   | mystery | spy       | epic        | drama    |
| Sport         | cycling | badminton | volleyball  | handball |

