.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-8::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: board-games, camping, cooking, sudoku
House: farmhouse, art-deco, craftsman, gothic-revival
4 different pets are kept: hamster, horse, lizard, rabbit
1. the gothic-revival house is on the right of the owner of the hamster##1
2. the art-deco house is between the owner of the rabbit and the person who's hobby is camping##2
3. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the right of the owner of the lizard##1
4. the owner of the lizard is on the right of the owner of the hamster##1
5. the gothic-revival house is on the right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
6. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the left of the craftsman house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |    3    |      4      |
| Hobby         | sudoku  | camping | cooking | board-games |
| House   | farmhouse  | gothic-revival | art-deco   | craftsman         |
| Pet           | hamster | lizard  | horse   | rabbit      |

