.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-15::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: baking, chess, fishing, skydiving
The people have 4 different jobs:  paramedic, police-officer, project-manager, security-guard
4 different pets are kept: bird, turtle, ferret, dog
1. the person who's hobby is fishing is the owner of the ferret##1
2. the owner of the dog is the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
3. the person who's hobby is baking is the security-guard##1
4. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the far left##1
5. the owner of the turtle is between the paramedic and the person who's hobby is baking##2
6. the project-manager is on the left of the owner of the bird##1
7. the owner of the bird is between the owner of the dog and the owner of the turtle##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |        2        |       3        |       4        |
| Hobby   | fishing   | chess           | baking         | skydiving      |
| Job     | paramedic | project-manager | security-guard | police-officer |
| Pet   | ferret     | turtle         | bird       | dog        |

