.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-20::.
There 4 different types of food: asparagus, cabbage, strawberry, watermelon
There are 4 different favourite colors: apricot, yellow, ebony, emerald
The people use 4 different means of transport: helicopter, jet-ski, motorbike, skateboard
1. the person who likes apricot is on the far left##1
2. the person eating asparagus is on the right of the person who likes yellow##1
3. the person driving the jet-ski is on the right of the person who likes apricot##1
4. the person eating strawberry is on the far right##1
5. the person driving the skateboard is the person who likes emerald##1
6. the person who likes yellow is between the person eating watermelon and the person driving the motorbike##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2    |     3     |     4      |
| Food        | watermelon | cabbage | asparagus | strawberry |
| Color         | apricot       | yellow     | ebony   | emerald   |
| Transport   | helicopter | jet-ski | motorbike | skateboard |

 